Use the standard library
This is how to factorize of n:
   Remember that factors is []
   Remember that d is 2

   Do this n times:
      When n is 1, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when

      Do this n times:
         When remainder of n and d is not 0, then:
            Leave the loop
         End when
         Add factors to d
         Remember that n is quotient of n and d
      End do

      Increase d
   End do

   The answer is factors
Now you know

>>> factorize of 8
[2, 2, 2]
>>> factorize of 25
[5, 5]
>>> factorize of 70
[2, 5, 7]